import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { Flex, Spacer, Box, Heading, Button } from '@chakra-ui/react';

const Header = () => {
	return(
		<Flex p='1' style={{backgroundColor: 'grey'}}>
			<Box p='2'>
				<Link to='/'>
					<Heading size='md'>Placeholder app</Heading>
				</Link>
			</Box>
			<Spacer />
			<Box>
				<Link to='/signup'>
					<Button colorScheme='teal' mr='4'>
						Sign up
					</Button>
				</Link>
				<Link to='/login'>
					<Button colorScheme='teal'>Log in</Button>
				</Link>
				<Link to='signupform'>
					<Button colorScheme='teal' ml='4'>Signup Form</Button>
				</Link>
			</Box>
		</Flex>
	)
}

export default Header;
